[SN]TITLE[SN]
Storms and showers hit Wales

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
More lightning, rain and wind is thought to be in store after a weekend of intense downpours.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
South-west Wales was the worst hit, with several flooding incidents in Pembrokeshire and Ceredigion.
It followed a yellow "be aware" warning for the South Wales coast.
But storms can make for a good picture, here are some of your weather photos from around Wales.
